The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Lanka ex-PM 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Lanka ex-PM 
                            
	Chennai, Nov. 20: CPI cadres today gheraoed former Sri Lankan Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe on his way back from a temple in Thiruvarur district. CPI workers were protesting against the Lankan army for killing innocent Tamils.         
	Police later escorted him to Madurai, from where he flew to Chennai.                                                                                                                                                                          
